description: All attempts to probe the mysteries of Belasco House have ended in murder, suicide, or insanity, and this newest investigation into its secrets of life and death is no different. The foursome is about to learn that the house does not give up its secrets willingly, or without tragic consequence. The conclusion to IDW's gripping adaptation of the classic Richard Matheson novel!
